collation.signatures:
   Quire marks in undecorated Ethiopic numerals written in black ink:
   ፯ in the upper right corner of fols. 55v, ;
  ፰ in the upper right corner of 63v, ;
  ፱ in the upper left corner of 64r, 
cut off Gǝʿǝz numeral, probably ፲፩ in the upper right corner of 87v, ;
   ፲፪ in the upper right corner of 95v, ;
   ፲፫ in the upper left corner of 96r
